1. update ssh-key:
    ssh-keygen
    ssh-add

2. ssh remote connect:
    add .ssh/id_rsa.pub into target machine .ssh/authorized_keys

3. github
    test whether ssh to github:
        ssh git@ssh.github.com
    sometimes firewall do not allow all ssh functions.
    solutions: ssh over https
        ssh -p 443 git@ssh.github.com
